{"tid":2114004,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"睇得出風向開始賴市民唔自律，掩蓋支那源頭","createTime":"2020-07-18T13:13:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T13:19:41.000Z","uid":273218,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9fe77d6bcdd3b30487fa2677cc8d0ec50061c353","tid":2114004,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T13:13:45.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打出post,依家再推<br />\n保安局發出左超過20萬張豁免強制檢疫<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2102947/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2102947/page/1</a><br />\n請大家支持廣傳消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔自救大家玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋可以做咩嘢？<br />\n1.話比身邊嘅人知香港有個後門大量吸收潛在冇病症感染者及傳播者。<br />\n<br />\n2.呼籲身邊所有人戴口罩，特別係果班唔肯帶嘅中年人<br />\n<br />\n3.如果身邊有料，可以報上傳媒比如蘋果。<br />\n例如喺之前post有其他人話知道：<br />\n灣仔入境個邊D移民公司而家當免檢疫証明係生意咁做，搵班阿姐派傳單幫人攪。<br />\n每日中港司機都幾千人出出入入。<br />\n<br />\n4.煲大件事！比全世界多D人知道，只有多D人覺醒，知道個政府係棄全香港巿民安危不顧，先會爭取到更多人企係我哋呢邊，同我哋一齊抗疫！<br />\n<br />\n兄弟姊妹各自爬山 他日平安相聚<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e74406b4774adee3407fe5cb5ec26e9d8802590","tid":2114004,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T13:14:17.000Z","msg":"（有圖）呢幅圖解釋左點解咁多本地個案<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2104743\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2104743</a>"},{"pid":"cec0b715fd29f635effdf93bbc0112712fb8b274","tid":2114004,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T13:14:50.000Z","msg":"支那大爆發: 睇下港共豁免左邊32類人士免受強制檢疫<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2097830\" data-auto-link tar